descriptor.originalquery: select tm.MISSION, concat('MRN_SPE22#',tm.MISSION,'####Mis4Pdf') GEN_PDF, concat('MRN_SPE22#',tm.MISSION,'####Mis4Pdf2') PDF2, IF((SELECT COUNT(tuj2.LOC) FROM MRQR_TRANSPORT_UNIT_JOURNEY tuj2 where tuj2.OMU_ID=tmv.OMU_ID and tuj2.LOCATION_PURPOSE = 'DES') > 1, (SELECT max(concat('MRN_SPE03#07#',tuj3.LOC_DESC))FROM MRQR_TRANSPORT_UNIT_JOURNEY tuj3 where tuj3.OMU_ID=tmv.OMU_ID and tuj3.LOCATION_PURPOSE = 'DES' ORDER BY tuj3.ETA DESC), (SELECT max(concat('MRN_SPE03#05#',tuj3.LOC_DESC))FROM MRQR_TRANSPORT_UNIT_JOURNEY tuj3 where tuj3.OMU_ID=tmv.OMU_ID and tuj3.LOCATION_PURPOSE = 'DES' ORDER BY tuj3.ETA DESC)) DES, concat('MRN_SPE01#TRPREQ&arg2=',tm.MISSION) TRPREQ, concat('MRN_SPE16#',a.ASSET,'#',a.ASSET) ASSET, concat('MRN_SPE01#ASSETA&arg1=',a.ASSET) ASSETA, concat('MRN_SPE04#L#MRN_SPE06#40#MRN_SPE07#- ',n.DESCRIPTION,'#- ',n.ALB) NSN_DESC_ALB, MIN(tuj.ETA) START, MAX(tuj.ETA) END, f.WSC FROM MRQR_ASSETS a join mrqr_nsn n on a.nsn = n.nsn join MRQR_TRANSPORT_MISSIONS_VEHICLES tmv on tmv.VEHICLE = a.ASSET join MRQR_TRANSPORT_MISSIONS tm on tm.MISSION=tmv.MISSION join MRQR_TRANSPORT_UNIT_JOURNEY tuj on tuj.OMU_ID=tmv.OMU_ID join MRQR_FUNCTIONS f on f.function=a.function WHERE a.TPTMOBCTR='pVKEYD' and (tm.ENDDATE BETWEEN DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL -1 DAY) and DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL +14 DAY) OR tm.STARTDATE BETWEEN DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL -1 DAY) and DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL +14 DAY) OR (tm.STARTDATE<=DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL -1 DAY) and CURDATE()>=DATE_ADD(CURDATE(), INTERVAL +14 DAY))) GROUP BY a.ASSET, a.DESCRIPTION, a.TPTMOBCTR, tm.MISSION, tm.STARTDATE, tm.ENDDATE, tmv.OMU_ID, f.WSC
